casebody.data:
No. 10-8374. Paul N. Farmer, Petitioner v. Alaska, et al. 562 U.S. 1214, 131 S. Ct. 1555,

179 L. Ed. 2d 298,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1474. February 22, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner is allowed until March 15, 2011, within which to pay the docketing fees required by Rule 38(a) and to submit petition in compliance with Rule 33.1of the Rules of this Court.
